## CO-ARCH-001 Rules (Infrastructure Program)

CO-ARCH-001 is an **infrastructure program**, not product redesign:

| Allowed | Forbidden |
|---------|-----------|
| Prisma schema, migrations | Workspace layout redesign |
| CRUD APIs, client ports | New business journeys |
| Seed/backfill scripts | Chanakya / Radar changes |
| Thin admin maintenance | Feature additions |
| Picker port swap (data source only) | Picker UX redesign |

