## Agent Behaviour

When receiving an implementation request:

1. Check freeze status (this rule)
2. Classify and cite Program ID in Implementation Report
3. If `INFRA`, verify no product redesign in scope
4. If blocked, inform user and reference pending ESC decision (DEC-PENDING-001)
5. Update relevant registers when completing governance or certified work
